Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫那种名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这才是你真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽  玛丽·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽·帕法西？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽  玛丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的幻觉是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖跟我们走吧  E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉  您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  阿里路亚  没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽明明就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亚  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亚  阿里路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽  我一定会来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam有三台？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要优先确保设施的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam脱离  开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务结束  任务结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼  总算结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们成功救出同志了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多亏了GIN1的情报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳  我听过参加救援部队的成员的报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说其中一位成员在设施中目击到了阿萨迪斯坦第一公主\N玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛…玛丽娜她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被囚禁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我们没能救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根据报告  玛丽娜公主被疑似Celestial Being的成员带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走了？  被Celestial Being？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜…
